description: A collection of circles in a perfectly circular formation with a perpendicular cross of circles within it and six diamond-shaped equidistant formations of circles surrounding the main circular formation. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a pale pink triangle at the top of the circular formation and a very pale purplish-blue triangle on the right side of the circular formation.
